<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible", content="ie=edge")
    title 회원가입:: NEWBELL 
  body
    include ../public/pug/nav/nav.pug
    main
      section.item-flex.flex-all-center.register-wrap.low
        div.col-lg-3.col-md-4.col-sm-6.col-xs-8.register-form.item-flex.flex-direction-column
          div.item-flex.flex-all-center.brand-logo
            img.brand-logo-img(src="public/img/logo.png", alt="NEWBELL LOGO") 
          div.register-content
            form(action='/register' method='post') 
              div.form-group
                input.form-control(type='text' name='name' placeholder='이름')  
              div.form-group
                input.form-control(type='email' name='email' placeholder='이메일')  
              div.form-group
                input.form-control#password(type='password' placeholder='비밀번호(영문,숫자 포함 8글자 이상)')
              div.form-group
                input.form-control#verifyPW(type='password' name='pw' placeholder='비밀번호확인')
              div.form-group
                input.form-control(type='phone' name='phone' placeholder='휴대폰번호(-를 빼고 기입하세요)')
              div.news-send.item-flex.flex-align-center
                input(type='checkbox' id='checkbox') 
                label(for='checkbox')
                span 뉴벨의 새로운 소식을 받습니다. 
              div.register-finish-btn-wrap.item-flex.flex-all-center
                a(href="/register")
                  button(type='submit') 회원가입완료 